EN: In this court, they will each make their rulings from their own perspectives.

ZH: 想让争议停止，我们需要一个裁定者来解决。
EN: To put an end to the dispute, we need an arbitrator to make a ruling.

ZH: 我们需要一个第三方来裁定这个争端。
EN: We need a third party to arbitrate this dispute.

